description:
When Heroes was first announced, there was a bit of resistance from the church community. After all, how was a video game supposed to help address the spiritual needs of the church?

Vanesa talks with Pastor Sam Gungaloo to find out about the challenges behind the making of Heroes. Faced with the seemingly impossible, Sam learned that impossibility was just a challenge to rise up to.

Learn more at: https://www.heroesbibletrivia.org/en/
